### 1. 注册用户
POST http://localhost:8080/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account": "student",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "张三",
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "email": "test@qq.com",
  "role": "user",
  "status": 1,
  "remark": "注册测试"
}

### 2. 登录 → 自动获取 token
POST http://localhost:8080/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account": "student",
  "password": "123456"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("token", response.body.data.token);
%}

### 3. 景区列表
GET http://localhost:8080/spot/list
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 景区详情（id=1）
GET http://localhost:8080/spot/detail?id=1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 景区名称下拉列表
GET http://localhost:8080/spot/nameList
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ====================== 酒店模块（需登录）======================
### 6. 酒店列表
GET http://localhost:8080/hotel/list
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. 酒店详情（id=1）
GET http://localhost:8080/hotel/detail?id=1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. 酒店名称下拉列表
GET http://localhost:8080/hotel/nameList
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}